ActDepartment of Human Resources and Skills Development Act
PrecisAppointment of LINDA LIZOTTE-MacPHERSON of Kanata, Ontario, as Associate Deputy Minister of Human Resources and Skills Development to be styled Senior Associate Deputy Minister of Human Resources and Skills Development and Chief Operating Officer for Service Canada during pleasure; and as a commissioner of the Canada Employment Insurance Commission who shall be the Vice-Chairperson of the Commission, effective January 5, 2009.
